ConfluenceVelocityResourceCache caches velocity resources uses the path to the resource as a cache key. Given that the same resource can be identified by relative or absolute path it be cached several times. In general the same path can be written in many different ways ( if ./ or ../ are used) and therefore the same resource can be cached under many different keys.

